data.description: This wonderful three bedroom, two bathroom home features a split floor plan, open living room and kitchen concept, and plenty of fully fenced backyard for entertaining on the patio. You are welcomed by a spacious entryway, perfect for all your bookshelves and collectables, leading into the separate laundry room - complete with washer and dryer included. This house has been well maintained and requires very little upkeep. Perfect starter home right in the middle of town! Come take a look!
